00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:35,074
I chose a local medical university here.

296
00:19:35,730 --> 00:19:36,876
Wait.

297
00:19:37,727 --> 00:19:38,789
What about...

298
00:19:40,112 --> 00:19:41,297
those boxes?

299
00:19:41,957 --> 00:19:43,016
Oh, that.

300
00:19:43,734 --> 00:19:44,917
