309
00:20:08,374 --> 00:20:09,608
Those punks...

310
00:20:10,788 --> 00:20:12,152
totally got me fooled.

311
00:20:21,645 --> 00:20:22,997
By the way, Minato-san,

312
00:20:24,248 --> 00:20:26,317
