00:21:24,567 --> 00:21:25,774
Finally.

319
00:21:28,034 --> 00:21:29,755
I'm so happy for them.

320
00:21:34,713 --> 00:21:35,777
Shuu-kun.

321
00:21:37,070 --> 00:21:38,136
Maybe love...

322
00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:41,834
