333
00:22:49,047 --> 00:22:50,469
It was just half a year.

334
00:22:50,516 --> 00:22:52,605
All right. I got it.
Just calm down.

335
00:23:01,947 --> 00:23:04,465
Jeez, I'm all wet again.

336
00:23:04,737 --> 00:23:06,410
It's all your fault.

337
00:23:10,115 --> 00:23:11,152
Shin.

338
00:23:12,355 --> 00:23:14,160
How about drying your clothes at my place?

339
00:23:16,462 --> 00:23:17,801
Are you leading me on?

